data.description: NEW ROOF INSTALLED JANUARY 10TH! BEAUTIFUL 3 BED 2 BATH 2 CAR GARAGE, HOME IN THE HIGHLY SOUGHT AFTER WALDEN ON LAKE CONROE! THIS HOME FEATURES A COZY LIVING AREA, WOOD BURNING FIREPLACE, STAINLESS STEEL APPLIANCES IN KITCHEN WITH TILE FLOORING AND GRANITE COUNTERTOPS. PRIMARY BATH HAS DOUBLE SINKS, SEPARATE SHOWER/SOAK TUB, DECORATIVE LIGHT IN PRIMARY BEDROOM. GOOD SIZED SECONDARY BEDROOMS, BACKYARD IS GREAT FOR ENTERTAINING WITH STONE BBQ, LARGE DECK & COVERED PATIO. A LAKE & GOLF COURSE COMMUNITY, PARKS, POOLS, MARINA, TENNIS. SCHEDULE YOUR VIEWING TODAY!
